#  4 SIG_GLOB .... Global significance or part of all pixels to fit .............
#  5 GOOD ........ Global goodness or number of equal parts of pixels ...........
#  6 DUST_TEMP ... Derived dust temperature of source or pixel .................. K
#  7 TEMP_ERRO ... Uncertainty of derived temperature ........................... K
#  8 TOTL_MASS ... Derived total mass (gas+dust) of source ...................... Msun
#  9 MASS_ERRO ... Uncertainty of derived mass from SED fitting ................. Msun
# 10 MASS_ERRT ... Total mass uncertainty (incl. distance opacity dust/gas) ..... Msun
# 11 BOLO_LUMI ... Derived bolometric luminosity ................................ Lsun
# 12 LUMI_ERRO ... Uncertainty of derived luminosity ............................ Lsun
# 13 SLD_ANGLE ... Derived solid angle (diameter) ............................... arcsec
# 14 ANGL_ERRO ... Uncertainty of derived solid angle ........................... arcsec
# 15 SURFACE_D ... Derived surface density of source or pixel ................... cm^-2
# 16 SURFD_ERR ... Uncertainty of derived surface density ....................... cm^-2
